%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Rs%2010%2C000%20Crores'%3A%20In%20a%20Poll%20Year%2C%20a%20PDS%20Scam%20Once%20Again%20Poses%20Corruption%20Hurdle%20for%20TMC%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F11135848%2FUntitled-design-10-1.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3EKolkata%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EOn%20January%208%20(Monday)%2C%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20(ED)%20alleged%20extensive%20corruption%20within%20the%20West%20Bengal%20public%20distribution%20system%20(PDS)%20scam.%20ED%20sources%20estimated%20that%20a%20single%20suspect%2C%20Shankar%20Adhya%2C%20the%20former%20chairman%20of%20Bongaon%20Municipality%20and%20a%20close%20aide%20of%20the%20arrested%20minister%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindubusinessline.com%2Fnews%2Fed-arrests-west-bengal-minister-jyotipriya-mullick-in-pds-irregularities-case%2Farticle67467231.ece%5C%22%3EJyotipriya%20Mallick%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20could%20be%20responsible%20for%20embezzling%20up%20to%20Rs%2010%2C000%20crores.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20the%20critical%20general%20election%20approaches%2C%20the%20ration%20scam%2C%20involving%20thousands%20of%20crores%2C%20adds%20to%20the%20embarrassment%20for%20chief%20minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20and%20senior%20TMC%20leaders.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fother-states%2Fmagnitude-of-the-10000-crore-pds-scam-in-west-bengal-is-enormous-ed%2Farticle67720001.ece%5C%22%3EED%20submissions%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Adhya%20played%20a%20direct%20role%20in%20laundering%20approximately%20Rs%2010%2C000%20crores%20through%20foreign%20currency%20trading%20and%20exchange%20in%20the%20border%20areas%20of%20the%20state%2C%20with%20nearly%20half%20of%20that%20sum%20stemming%20from%20the%20ration%20distribution%20scam.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20The%20agency%20claimed%20in%20court%20that%20Adhya%20managed%20to%20smuggle%20out%20over%20Rs%202%2C500%20crores%20to%20Dubai%20through%20forex%20trade.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fkolkata%2Fday-after-attack-on-ed-officials-hunt-begins-for-tmc-leader-sheikh-shahjahan%2Farticleshow%2F106603062.cms%5C%22%3ESheikh%20Shahjahan%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20other%20key%20suspect%2C%20remains%20at%20large%20despite%20an%20ED%20look-out%20circular%20(LOC)%20issued%20for%20him.%20The%20LOC%20was%20issued%20after%20an%20armed%20mob%20attacked%20investigating%20agencies%20during%20a%20raid%20in%20Sandeshkhali%2C%20North%2024%20Parganas%2C%20last%20Friday%20(January%205).%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EWhat%20is%20the%20ration%20scam%20in%20West%20Bengal%3F%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDuring%20the%20COVID-19%20lockdown%20in%20May%202020%2C%20protests%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fcities%2Fkolkata%2Faccused-of-irregularities-in-pds-ration-dealers-house-ransacked-in-murshidabad-6391017%2F%5C%22%3Eerupted%20in%20West%20Bengal%3C%2Fa%3E%20over%20alleged%20irregularities%20in%20the%20distribution%20of%20PDS%20grains.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20first%20information%20report%20(FIR)%20was%20filed%20in%20Nadia%20district.%20Then-governor%20of%20West%20Bengal%20Jagdeep%20Dhankhar%20(now%20vice%20president)%2C%20and%20the%20central%20government%20had%20criticised%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20handling%20of%20the%20PDS.%20On%20April%2023%2C%202020%2C%20the%20Centre%20informed%20the%20state%20that%20food%20grain%20distribution%20was%20non-existent%20under%20the%20Pradhan%20Mantri%20Garib%20Kalyan%20Anna%20Yojana%20(PMGKAY).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fin-bengals-sandeshkhali-controversial-tmc-leader-sheikh-shahjahans-hold-is-powerful%5C%22%3E%20In%20Bengal%E2%80%99s%20Sandeshkhali%2C%20Controversial%20TMC%20Leader%20Sheikh%20Shahjahan%E2%80%99s%20Hold%20Is%20Powerful%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fexplained%2Fed-crpf-attacked-west-bengal-pds-scam-9098098%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EIndian%20Express%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20under%20PMGKAY%2C%20each%20ration%20card%20holder%20was%20entitled%20to%205%20kilogram%20of%20food%20grains%20and%201%20kg%20of%20pulses%2C%20in%20addition%20to%20the%20monthly%20quota%20of%205%20kg%20of%20subsidised%20food%20grains%20per%20person%20under%20the%20National%20Food%20Security%20Act%20(NFSA).%20Investigations%20revealed%20that%20an%20influential%20businessman%2C%20Bakibur%20Rahman%2C%20supplied%20rice%20and%20wheat%20in%20insufficient%20quantities%20to%20fair%20price%20shop%20distributors.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBakibur%2C%20allegedly%20supported%20by%20Mallick%2C%20a%20powerful%20minister%20close%20to%20the%20chief%20minister%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eprofited%20by%20selling%20the%20excess%20grain%20in%20the%20open%20market.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EED%20sources%20claim%20that%20flour%20mill%20owners%20supplied%20less%20flour%20to%20distributors%20than%20paid%20for%20by%20the%20government.%20Mill%20owners%20claimed%20that%20for%20the%20price%20of%201%20kg%20of%20flour%2C%20government%20suppliers%20received%20only%20about%20600%20grams.%20Approximately%2030%25%20of%20the%20PDS%20ration%20intended%20for%20beneficiaries%20in%20West%20Bengal%20was%20redirected%20to%20the%20open%20market.%20In%20collaboration%20with%20some%20local%20leaders%20from%20the%20ruling%20party%2C%20rice%20millers%20created%20fake%20bank%20accounts%20for%20farmers%2C%20siphoning%20off%20the%20minimum%20support%20price%20(MSP)%20earmarked%20for%20paddy%20growers.%20Rice%20millers%20earned%20nearly%20Rs%20200%20per%20quintal%20for%20grains%20that%20government%20agencies%20were%20supposed%20to%20procure%20at%20MSP%20from%20farmers%2C%20of%20which%2C%20a%20significant%20percentage%20had%20allegedly%20to%20be%20shared%20with%20Mallick%2C%20who%20oversaw%20the%20Food%20and%20Supplies%20Ministry%20in%20the%20previous%20TMC%20government%20from%202016%20to%202021.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fpartha-chatterjee-ssc-scam-tmc-manata-corruption%5C%22%3EPartha%20Chatterjee%2C%20another%20major%20leader%20currently%20in%20jail%2C%20had%20to%20lose%20his%20portfolio%3C%2Fa%3E%20after%20his%20involvement%20in%20the%20job%20recruitment%20scam%20came%20to%20light%2C%20Mallick%20continues%20to%20remain%20a%20minister%20holding%20key%20position%20in%20the%20cabinet.%20Similarly%2C%20Shahjahan%20and%20Adhya%2C%20crucial%20figures%20in%20TMC%E2%80%99s%20electoral%20strategy%20in%20North%2024%20Parganas%2C%20continue%20to%20enjoy%20party%20support%20despite%20being%20confronted%20with%20accusations%20spanning%20from%20financial%20misconduct%20to%20homicide.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERecently%2C%20Shovandev%20Chattopadhyay%2C%20a%20seasoned%20TMC%20leader%2C%20cautioned%20that%20ED%20officials%20can%20anticipate%20similar%20resistance%20from%20TMC%20student%20activists%20in%20the%20days%20ahead%2C%20leading%20to%20public%20outcry.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDuring%20the%20panchayat%20elections%20in%202013%2C%202018%2C%20and%202023%2C%20opposition%20parties%20struggled%20to%20field%20candidates%20in%20the%20Sadeshkhali%20blocks%2C%20where%20Shahjahan%20wields%20significant%20political%20influence.%20Likewise%2C%20Adhya%E2%80%99s%20influence%20in%20the%20Matua-dominated%20border%20areas%20near%20Bangaon%20became%20evident%20when%20ED%20officials%20encountered%20resistance%20from%20his%20supporters.%20Following%20his%20arrest%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Emany%20locals%20came%20forward%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fer-tmc-councillor-said-in-bangaon-985709.html%5C%22%3Edisclosed%3C%2Fa%3E%20his%20involvement%20in%20corruption%2C%20intimidation%2C%20and%20violence%20to%20the%20local%20media%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20corruption%20in%20ration%20distribution%20poses%20a%20threat%20to%20the%20TMC%20organisation%20as%20there%20are%20tens%20of%20Shahjahan%20within%20the%20party.%20Their%20potential%20arrests%20could%20exert%20pressure%20on%20the%20party%2C%20leading%20to%20a%20cascading%20effect%20on%20its%20influence%2C%E2%80%9D%20observed%20political%20analyst%20Biswanath%20Chakraborty.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fpartha-chatterjee-ssc-scam-tmc-manata-corruption%5C%22%3ETMC%20May%20Have%20Sacked%20Partha%20Chatterjee%2C%20But%20Its%20Problems%20With%20Corruption%20Run%20Deep%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20part%20of%20the%20collusion%2C%20ration%20dealers%20were%20compelled%20to%20contribute%20a%20portion%20of%20their%20monthly%20earnings%20to%20the%20local%20syndicate%20in%20exchange%20for%20the%20windfall.%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20spoke%20to%20a%20ration%20dealer%20in%20Murshidabad%2C%20whose%20identity%20is%20being%20withheld%20for%20protection.%20The%20dealer%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20amount%20of%20money%20we%E2%80%99re%20paying%20as%20bribe%20and%20commission%20to%20the%20local%20syndicate%20kept%20on%20increasing.%20Many%20of%20us%20felt%20the%20dealership%20was%20not%20profitable%20anymore.%20I%20applied%20three%20years%20back%20to%20return%20my%20licence%2C%20but%20it%20was%20not%20accepted.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20a%20family%20of%20five%2C%20each%20with%20ration%20cards.%20Yet%2C%20we%20receive%20only%2012%20kgs%20of%20rice%20every%20month%20from%20the%20ration%20shop.%20I%20use%20ration%20cards%20from%20other%20families%20who%20do%20not%20want%20to%20eat%20this%20rice%2C%20but%20are%20eligible%20for%20rations.%20I%20pay%20them%20Rs%2025%20per%20kg%20for%20their%20share%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Tapan%20Roy%2C%20a%20part-time%20transport%20worker%20from%20Dhupguri%20in%20North%20Bengal.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%202007%2C%20during%20the%20tenure%20of%20the%20Buddhadeb%20Bhattacharjee-led%20Left%20Front%20government%2C%20protests%20erupted%20over%20alleged%20irregularities%20in%20the%20public%20distribution%20system.%20One%20of%20the%20demonstrations%2C%20marked%20by%20violence%2C%20resulted%20in%20the%20death%20of%20Ayub%20Sheikh%2C%20a%20protester%2C%20in%20a%20clash%20with%20the%20police.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20recently%20visited%20Ayub%E2%80%99s%20family%2C%20who%20now%20claim%20to%20have%20received%20insufficient%20rations.%20Jhunafa%20Bibi%2C%20Ayub%E2%80%99s%20wife%2C%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CSometimes%20the%20rice%20arrives%20in%20a%20month%2C%20sometimes%20it%20doesn%E2%80%99t.%20Kerosene%20is%20unavailable.%20Previously%2C%20lentils%20were%20accessible%3B%20now%20there%20are%20none.%20Wheat%20flour%20arrives%20irregularly%2C%20and%20the%20quality%20is%20very%20poor!%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ETranslated%20from%20Bangla%20to%20English%20by%20Aparna%20Bhattacharya.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704963057000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F11135848%2FUntitled-design-10-1.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Frs-10000-crores-in-a-poll-year-a-pds-scam-once-again-poses-corruption-hurdle-for-tmc%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22As%20the%20critical%20general%20election%20approaches%2C%20the%20situation%2C%20involving%20thousands%20of%20crores%2C%20adds%20to%20the%20embarrassment%20for%20chief%20minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20and%20senior%20TMC%20leaders.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22As%20a%20Classical%20Musician%2C%20Rashid%20Khan%20Showed%20His%20Brilliance%20at%20a%20Very%20Young%20Age%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F11130712%2FUntitled-design-9-1.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EUstad%20Rashid%20Khan%20was%20the%20great%20grandson%20of%20Rampur-Sehaswan%20Gharana%20founder%20Enayat%20Hussain%20Khan.%20He%20did%20his%20lineage%20proud.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGone%20too%20soon%20at%2055%2C%20when%20some%20musicians%20reach%20a%20plateau%2C%20he%20could%20have%20continued%20to%20evolve%20because%20of%20his%20fertile%20mind.%20The%20coming%20together%20of%20voice%2C%20style%2C%20fluid%20%3Cem%3Etaans%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20reposeful%20%3Cem%3Eaalaap%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20made%20him%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fthe-arts%2Fustad-rashid-khan-murad-ali-tribute%5C%22%3Erare%20and%20complete%20musician%3C%2Fa%3E.%20He%20lacked%20nothing%20in%20any%20area%20of%20his%20field%20and%20beyond%2C%20as%20he%20even%20ventured%20into%20film%20music.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20knew%20Rashid%20from%20my%20two%20years%20tenure%20at%20Sangeet%20Research%20Academy%2C%20where%20we%20were%20both%20%E2%80%98scholars%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%93%20the%20term%20for%20scholarship%20holders%20%E2%80%93%20he%20under%20Ustad%20Nisar%20Hussain%20Khan%20and%20I%20under%20Pandita%20Girija%20Devi%20%3Cem%3Eji%3C%2Fem%3E.%20SRA%20carries%20forward%20the%20%3Cem%3Eguru-shishya%20parampara%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%93%20the%20tradition%20of%20teacher%20and%20student%20relationships.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20as%20a%20%E2%80%98scholar%E2%80%99%2C%20he%20was%20considered%20a%20maestro%20by%20the%20gurus%20at%20SRA%20%E2%80%93%20Pandit%20A.%20Kanan%20who%20represented%20Kirana%20Gharana%E2%80%99s%20reposeful%20style%20and%20who%20I%20loved%20because%20he%20had%20a%20huge%20photograph%20of%20my%20Guru%20Begum%20Akhtar%20at%20the%20very%20entrance%20of%20his%20home%3B%20his%20wife%20Malavika%20Kanan%2C%20who%20said%20she%20never%20read%20any%20newspaper%20in%20the%20morning%20because%20all%20the%20bad%20news%20ruined%20her%20day%3B%20the%20stern-faced%20Ustad%20Nisar%20Hussain%20Khan%2C%20Rashid%E2%80%99s%20mentor%20and%20guru%2C%20a%20man%20of%20few%20words%20and%20an%20uncompromising%20demeanour%3B%20Pandit%20Jagdish%20Prasad%20whose%20wife%20would%20complain%20unabashedly%20that%20he%20kept%20her%20awake%20all%20night%3B%20Pandit%20Sunil%20Bose%20and%20Pandit%20Ajoy%20Chakraborty%20who%20was%20then%20a%20scholar-musician.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVijay%20Kichlu%20was%20at%20the%20helm%20of%20affairs%20as%20the%20director%20of%20SRA.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20jointly%20mentored%20and%20assessed%20each%20%E2%80%98scholar%E2%80%99%20once%20a%20week.%20About%20Rashid%2C%20they%20would%20say%20amongst%20themselves%2C%20%E2%80%9CWho%20are%20we%20to%20assess%20him%3F%20He%E2%80%99s%20our%20equal%2C%20not%20less%20than%20us%E2%80%9D.%20They%20too%20were%20in%20awe%20of%20his%20brilliance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20used%20to%20come%20over%20in%20the%20evenings%20to%20Girija%20Devi%20or%20%3Cem%3EAppa%20ji%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%98s%20house%20often%2C%20and%20would%20regale%20us%20with%20his%20mimicry.%20He%20used%20to%20do%20a%20hilarious%20Bharatnatyam%20%3Cem%3Ebhav-dikhana%3C%2Fem%3E%20act%20of%20a%20famous%20dancer%20and%20would%20have%20us%20all%20in%20splits.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20he%20had%20fallen%20madly%20in%20love%20with%20the%20woman%20who%20he%20eventually%20married%2C%20and%20was%20tortured%20by%20his%20guru%20%E2%80%98s%20command%20to%20marry%20his%20relative%20instead.%20At%20that%20time%2C%20I%20was%20his%20confidant.%20He%20would%20speak%20to%20me%20of%20his%20despair%20and%20complained%20bitterly%20that%20his%20guru%20would%20order%20him%20to%20run%20errands%20all%20morning%20when%20he%20wanted%20to%20do%20practice%20music%20instead.%20We%20shared%20grouses%20against%20our%20gurus%20and%20felt%20we%20were%20at%20their%20mercy.%20I%20found%20my%20guru%20unkind%20as%20I%20constantly%20compared%20her%20with%20my%20first%20guru%2C%20Begum%20Akhtar%2C%20who%20was%20extremely%20indulgent.%20Later%2C%20I%20loved%20Girija%20Devi%20too%2C%20as%20I%20am%20sure%20Rashid%20also%20came%20to%20love%20his%20guru.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERashid%20and%20I%20met%20backstage%20before%20one%20of%20his%20concerts%20some%20years%20later%20and%20he%20chided%20me%3A%20%E2%80%9CLook%20where%20I%20have%20reached%E2%80%A6why%20aren%E2%80%99t%20you%20better%20known%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20music%20shone%20through%20his%20profound%20honesty%2C%20which%20was%20reflected%20in%20his%20gaze%20towards%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EHere%20are%20four%20renditions%20by%20Rashid%20Khan%20chosen%20by%20Rekha%20Surya%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fshare%2Fr%2FpJMRHRid9G2b61RY%2F%3Fmibextid%3Dqi2Omg%5C%22%3E1%3C%2Fa%3E%20%7C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fshare%2Fr%2FDPsz6ALK8dLBecVC%2F%3Fmibextid%3Dqi2Omg%5C%22%3E2%3C%2Fa%3E%20%7C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fshare%2Fr%2F1Wihd34o1zkFraTe%2F%3Fmibextid%3Dqi2Omg%5C%22%3E3%3C%2Fa%3E%20%7C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fshare%2Fr%2FCQUpNMsRHbwsi45z%2F%3Fmibextid%3Dqi2Omg%5C%22%3E4%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EHindustani%20semi-classical%20singer%20Rekha%20Surya%20is%20the%20youngest%20disciple%20of%20Begum%20Akhtar%20and%20later%20trained%20under%20Girija%20Devi.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704961852000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F11130712%2FUntitled-design-9-1.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fthe-arts%2Fclassical-musician-rashid-khan-obituary%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20warm%20tribute%20to%20the%20singer%20who%20died%20at%20the%20young%20age%20of%2055.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in