%20the%20invitation%20to%20its%20three%20top%20leaders%20to%20attend%20the%20Ram%20temple%20consecration%20ceremony%20in%20Ayodhya%2C%20claiming%20it%20has%20exposed%20the%20party's%20inherent%20opposition%20to%20India's%20culture%20and%20Hindu%20religion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDue%20to%20its%20feelings%20of%20%26quot%3Bjealousy%2C%20malice%20and%20inferiority%20complex%26quot%3B%20towards%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20the%20Congress%20had%20gone%20to%20the%20extent%20of%20opposing%20the%20country%20and%20is%20now%20opposing%20God%2C%20BJP%20spokesperson%20Sudhanshu%20Trivedi%20told%20reporters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Ram%20temple%20in%20Ayodhya%20symbolises%20the%20highest%20values%20of%20Indian%20traditions%20and%20culture%2C%20he%20said%2C%20but%20for%20the%20Congress%20and%20other%20opposition%20parties%20with%20a%20similar%20mindset%20extremist%20politics%20is%20more%20important%2C%20he%20alleged.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Trivedi%20noted%20that%20Iqbal%20Ansari%2C%20the%20Muslim%20litigant%20in%20the%20land%20dispute%20case%20involving%20the%20temple%20and%20the%20Babri%20mosque%20which%20one%20stood%20there%2C%20was%20also%20extended%20an%20invite%20which%20he%20has%20accepted%20but%20it%20is%20the%20Congress%20which%20has%20chosen%20to%20boycott%20the%20ceremony.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20claimed%20that%20it%20has%20been%20the%20main%20opposition%20party's%20tendency%20to%20create%20hurdle%20during%20historic%20moments%20for%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhenever%20the%20page%20of%20history%20turns%2C%20the%20Congress%20instead%20of%20standing%20with%20it%20has%20opted%20to%20boycott%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20citing%20a%20host%20of%20events%2C%20including%20the%20inauguration%20of%20the%20new%20Parliament%20building%2C%20enactment%20of%20the%20GST%2C%20presidential%20addresses%20to%20Parliament%20by%20Ram%20Nath%20Kovind%20and%20Droupadi%20Murmu.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPeople%20have%20also%20continued%20to%20keep%20the%20Congress%20away%20from%20power%20but%20it%20is%20not%20getting%20any%20wiser%2C%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20the%20party%20had%20an%20opportunity%20to%20redeem%20its%20past%20mistakes%20but%20it%20has%20wasted%20the%20chance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20rejected%20the%20Congress'%20contention%20that%20the%20BJP%20and%20the%20RSS%20had%20appropriated%20the%20entire%20event%2C%20scheduled%20for%20January%2022%20in%20Ayodhya%2C%20saying%20there%20is%20no%20division%20among%20people%20in%20the%20temple.%20It%20should%20not%20be%20linked%20to%20any%20organisation%20or%20ideology%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20spokesperson%20wondered%20if%20the%20Congress%20still%20stands%20with%20the%20idea%20of%20rebuilding%20the%20mosque%2C%20which%20was%20torn%20down%20by%20a%20frenzied%20mob%20in%20Ayodhya%20in%201992.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENoting%20that%20the%20then%20prime%20minister%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%20was%20opposed%20to%20the%20association%20of%20President%20Rajendra%20Prasad%20and%20some%20leaders%20of%20the%20Congress%20with%20the%20rebuilding%20and%20inauguration%20of%20the%20Somnath%20temple%2C%20Trivedi%20claimed%20the%20Congress%20is%20continuing%20with%20his%20legacy%20and%20has%20disowned%20the%20'Ram%20Rajya'%20concept%20of%20Mahatma%20Gandhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20temple%20is%20coming%20up%20after%20500%20years%20of%20struggle%20and%20has%20stirred%20national%20pride%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECongress%20leaders%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%2C%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20and%20Adhir%20Ranjan%20Chowdhury%20on%20Wednesday%20%26quot%3Brespectfully%20declined%26quot%3B%20the%20invitation%20to%20attend%20the%20Ram%20Temple%20consecration%20ceremony%2C%20with%20the%20party%20accusing%20the%20BJP%20of%20making%20it%20into%20a%20%26quot%3Bpolitical%20project%26quot%3B%20for%20electoral%20gains.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syn