0that%20he%20was%20unwell%20and%20had%20been%20admitted%20to%20the%20hospital.%20No%20one%20was%20found%20upon%20arriving%20at%20the%20hospital%2C%20and%20the%20doctor%20informed%20me%20that%20he%20had%20died.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUpon%20getting%20information%20about%20the%20incident%2C%20the%20police%20reached%20the%20spot%20and%20collected%20information%20regarding%20it.%20The%20police%20took%20possession%20of%20the%20body%20and%20sent%20it%20for%20a%20post-mortem.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChakia%20police%20station%20in-charge%20Dhananjay%20Kumar%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BAfter%20getting%20information%20about%20the%20incident%2C%20he%20reached%20the%20hospital%20with%20the%20police%20force%20and%20found%20the%20dead%20body.%20The%20body%20of%20the%20student%20was%20sent%20for%20a%20post-mortem.%20No%20application%20has%20been%20received%20yet%20from%20the%20family%20members%20of%20the%20deceased%20student.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20district%20education%20officer%2C%20Sanjay%20Kumar%2C%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20child's%20family%20members%20had%20beaten%20him.%20Due%20to%20this%2C%20he%20came%20to%20school%20without%20eating%20food%20and%20without%20wearing%20warm%20clothes.%20The%20post-mortem%20report%20will%20further%20reveal%20the%20reality%20of%20the%20incident.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20district%20education%20officer%2C%20Sanjay%20Kumar%2C%20collected%20information%20from%20BEO%20and%20BRP%20after%20the%20tragic%20incident.%20The%20headmasters%20of%20all%20the%20schools%20in%20the%20district%20were%20instructed%20to%20conduct%20class%20teacher%20awareness%20sessions%20in%20the%20classroom%20itself%20in%20case%20of%20a%20cold%20wave.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704960540000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ndtvimg.com%2Fi%2F2016-02%2Fs