0held%20by%20September%20this%20year%2C%20General%20Pande%20said%20the%20ceasefire%20understanding%20with%20Pak%20is%20holding%2C%20for%20now%2C%20along%20the%20Line%20of%20Control%20(LoC)%20despite%20the%20infiltration%20attempts.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704959760000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Fp96bl5rs_army-chief-general-manoj-pande_625x300_11_January_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Farmy-chief-general-manoj-panda-presser-our-adversaries-have-active-role-in-aiding-terror-in-j-k-army-chief-4841216%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22India's%20adversaries%20are%20playing%20an%20%26quot%3Bactive%20role%26quot%3B%20in%20aiding%20terrorists%20and%20terror-related%20activities%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir's%20Rajouri%20and%20Poonch%2C%20Army%20Chief%20General%20Manoj%20Pande%20said%20Thursday%2C%20in%20comments%20seen%20as%20referring%20to%20Pakistan's%20continuing%20suppor%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Farmy-chief-general-manoj-panda-presser-our-adversaries-have-active-role-in-aiding-terror-in-j-k-army-chief-4841216%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Farmy-chief-general-manoj-panda-presser-our-adversaries-have-active-role-in-aiding-terror-in-j-k-army-chief-4841216%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Farmy-chief-general-manoj-panda-presser-our-adversaries-have-active-role-in-aiding-terror-in-j-k-army-chief-4841216%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Watch%3A%20Virat%20Kohli!%20Who%3F%20Ronaldo%20says%20he%20is%20not%20'very%20popular'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704959565000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-106723441%2Cimgsize-38452.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Fnews%2Fwatch-virat-kohli-who-ronaldo-says-he-is-not-very-popular%2Farticleshow%2F106722800.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Virat%20Kohli%20has%20emerged%20as%20a%20global%20icon%2C%20captivating%20the%20hearts%20of%20fans%20across%20the%20world%20with%20his%20exceptional%20batting%20skills.%20Known%20for%20his%20remarkable%20ability%20to%20dominate%20bowlers%20from%20all%20corners%20of%20the%20globe%2C%20Virat%20has%20become%20a%20true%20inspiration%20for%20countless%20individuals.%20His%20sheer%20batting%20prowess%20and%20unwavering%20determination%20have%20propelled%20him%20to%20unimaginable%20heights%2C%20making%20him%20one%20of%20the%20most%20popular%20personalities%20in%20the%20world.%20But%20on%20Thursday%2C%20social%20media%20was%20shell-shocked%20after%20Brazilian%20football%20great%20Ronaldo%20refused%20to%20have%20heard%20Virat's%20name.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20SPORTS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Fnews%2Fwatch-virat-kohli-who-ronaldo-says-he-is-not-very-popular%2Farticleshow%2F106722800.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22World's%20Most%20Powerful%20Passports%3A%206%20Countries%20In%20Top%20Spot%2C%20India%20Ranks...%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFrance%2C%20Germany%2C%20Italy%2C%20Japan%2C%20Singapore%2C%20and%20Spain%20start%202024%20with%20the%20world's%20most%20powerful%20passport%2C%20allowing%20visa-free%20entry%20to%20194%20global%20destinations%2C%20according%20to%20the%20latest%20Henley%20Passport%20Index.%20The%20ranking%20is%20based%20on%20data%20from%20the%20International%20Air%20Transport%20Association%20(IATA).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20past%20five%20years%2C%20Japan%20and%20Singapore%20have%20consistently%20dominated%20the%20No.%201%20spot.%20However%2C%20this%20quarter's%20ranking%20showcases%20European%20nations%20jumping%20up%20the%20tanks.%20Finland%20and%20Sweden%20tied%20with%20South%20Korea%20in%20second%20place%2C%20offering%20visa-free%20access%20to%20193%20destinations.%20Austria%2C%20Denmark%2C%20Ireland%2C%20and%20the%20Netherlands%20secure%20the%20third%20position%2C%20providing%20passport%20holders%20access%20to%20192%20destinations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-80th-in-passport-index-full-list-of-countries-indians-can-visit-visa-free-maldives-mauritius-thailand-4840570%5C%22%3EIndia's%20passport%20ranked%2080th%3C%2Fa%3E%20spot%20in%20the%20list%2C%20with%20citizens%20allowed%20to%20travel%20to%2062%20countries%20without%20a%20visa%2C%20including%20popular%20tourist%20destinations%20like%20Indonesia%2C%20Malaysia%2C%20and%20Thailand.%20India%20shares%20its%20current%20rank%20with%20Uzbekistan%20while%20neighboring%20Pakistan%20is%20positioned%20at%20101st.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChristian%20H%20Kaelin%2C%20chairman%20of%20Henley%20%26amp%3B%20Partners%20and%20the%20creator%20of%20the%20passport%20index%20highlighted%20the%20widening%20global%20mobility%20gap%20between%20countries.%20Despite%20an%20overall%20trend%20toward%20increased%20travel%20freedom%20over%20the%20past%20two%20decades%2C%20the%20disparity%20between%20the%20top%20and%20bottom%20of%20the%20index%20has%20reached%20an%20all-time%20high.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kaelin%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20average%20number%20of%20destinations%20travelers%20are%20able%20to%20access%20visa-free%20has%20nearly%20doubled%20from%2058%20in%202006%20to%20111%20in%202024.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20emphasized%20that%20the%20top-ranked%20countries%20now%20enjoy%20the%20privilege%20of%20traveling%20to%20an%20astonishing%20166%20more%20destinations%20visa-free%20than%20Afghanistan%2C%20which%20occupies%20the%20bottom%20spot%20on%20the%20list%2C%20with%20access%20to%20just%2028%20countries%20without%20a%20visa.%20Syria%2C%20with%20visa-free%20access%20to%20only%2029%20destinations%2C%20holds%20the%20second-lowest%20position%2C%20followed%20by%20Iraq%20with%2031%20and%20Pakistan%20with%2034.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704959160000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2F7l399vpc_india-passport-getty_625x300_11_January_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fworlds-most-powerful-passports-6-countries-in-top-spot-india-ranks-4839816%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Worlds%20powerful%20passports%3A%20France%2C%20Germany%2C%20Italy%2C%20Japan%2C%20Singapore%2C%20and%20Spain%20start%202024%20with%20the%20worlds%20most%20powerful%20passport%2C%20allowing%20visa-free%20entry%20to%20194%20global%20destinations.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fworlds-most-powerful-passports-6-countries-in-top-spot-india-ranks-4839816%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fworlds-most-powerful-passports-6-countries-in-top-spot-india-ranks-4839816%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fworlds-most-powerful-passports-6-countries-in-top-spot-india-ranks-4839816%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Why%20Israel%20and%20Hezbollah%20Are%20Eager%20to%20Avoid%20a%20Full-Blown%20Regional%20War%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F02%2F15164743%2Ftaylor-brandon-Y8r0RTNrIWM-unsplash.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Fisraeli-strike-lebanon-kills-senior-commander-elite-hezbollah-unit-security-2024-01-08%2F%5C%22%3Ekilling%20of%20a%20Hezbollah%20commander%20in%20southern%20Lebanon%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Jan.%208%2C%202024%2C%20has%20raised%20concern%20that%20the%20conflict%20between%20Israel%20and%20Hamas%20could%20escalate%20into%20a%20regional%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWissam%20al-Tawil%2C%20the%20head%20of%20a%20unit%20that%20operates%20on%20Lebanon%E2%80%99s%20southern%20border%2C%20was%20killed%20in%20a%20targeted%20Israeli%20airstrike%20just%20days%20after%20a%20senior%20Hamas%20leader%20was%20assassinated%20in%20Beirut%20and%20amid%20sporadic%20attacks%20by%20Hezbollah%20on%20Israeli%20targets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20how%20likely%20is%20a%20full-scale%20conflict%20between%20Israel%20and%20Hezbollah%3F%20The%3Cem%3E%C2%A0Conversation%3C%2Fem%3E%20turned%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fkroc.nd.edu%2Ffaculty-and-staff%2Fasher-kaufman%2F%5C%22%3EAsher%20Kaufman%2C%20an%20expert%20on%20Lebanon-Israel%20relations%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Notre%20Dame%2C%20to%20assess%20what%20could%20happen%20next.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20do%20we%20know%20about%20the%20latest%20strike%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20know%20that%20it%20was%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnn.com%2F2024%2F01%2F08%2Fmiddleeast%2Fhezbollah-commander-killed-intl%2Findex.html%5C%22%3EIsraeli%20drone%20that%20killed%20al-Tawil%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Hezbollah%20has%20since%20released%20picture%20of%20him%20with%20Hassan%20Nasrallah%2C%20the%20group%E2%80%99s%20secretary%20general%2C%20and%20Qassem%20Soleiman%2C%20the%20former%20head%20of%20Quds%20Force%20%E2%80%93%20one%20of%20Iran%E2%80%99s%20main%20military%20branches%20%E2%80%93%20who%20was%20assassinated%20by%20the%20U.S.%20in%202020.%20This%20suggests%20that%20al-Tawil%20was%20a%20major%20target%20for%20Israel%2C%20as%20he%20clearly%20had%20connections%20with%20top%20figures%20in%20Lebanon%20and%20Iran.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20fact%20that%20it%20was%20a%20drone%20attack%20is%20also%20important.%20This%20suggests%20that%20the%20operation%20was%20based%20on%20good%20Israeli%20intelligence%20on%20al-Tawil%E2%80%99s%20whereabouts.%20This%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20a%20chance%20encounter.%20This%20was%20clearly%20a%20calculated%20and%20precise%20attack.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20operation%2C%20Israel%20said%20al-Tawil%20was%20responsible%20for%20a%20recent%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.timesofisrael.com%2Fidf-admits-mount-meron-air-traffic-control-base-damaged-in-hezbollah-attack%2F%5C%22%3Emissile%20attack%20on%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20Mount%20Meron%20intelligence%20base%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20northern%20Israel.%20That%20attack%20was%20in%20response%20to%20the%20earlier%20assassination%20of%20a%20Hamas%20leader%20in%20Beirut.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20what%20we%20are%20seeing%20is%20a%20pattern%20of%20tit-for-tat%20strikes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESo%20this%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20mark%20an%20escalation%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20don%E2%80%99t%20see%20the%20killing%20of%20al-Tawil%20as%20an%20escalation%2C%20as%20such.%20Rather%2C%20it%20is%20a%20targeted%20retaliation%20by%20Israel%20to%20the%20earlier%20Hezbollah%20strike%20on%20one%20of%20their%20facilities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20some%20important%20things%20to%20note%20in%20that%20regard.%20It%20was%20just%2010%20kilometers%20north%20of%20the%20Israel-Lebanon%20border.%20This%20is%20still%20within%20the%20geographical%20area%20where%20the%20two%20sides%20have%20been%20exchanging%20fire%20since%20the%20Oct.%207%20attack%20by%20Hamas%20in%20Israel.%20So%20this%20is%20still%20within%20the%20realm%20of%20border%20skirmishes%2C%20to%20my%20mind%2C%20and%20falls%20short%20of%20full%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIs%20it%20in%20the%20interests%20of%20Israel%20to%20escalate%20conflict%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20don%E2%80%99t%20think%20either%20side%20is%20interested%20in%20full-blown%20war%2C%20for%20different%20reasons.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Israel%2C%20the%20pressure%20is%20from%20outside%20the%20country.%20There%20is%20immense%20international%20pressure%20on%20Israel%20not%20to%20start%20a%20full-blown%20war%20with%20Hezbollah.%20Indeed%2C%20U.S.%20Secrtary%20of%20State%20Antony%20Blinken%20is%20currently%20in%20the%20region%20and%20visiting%20Israel%20with%20that%20message%3A%20Do%20not%20start%20a%20war%20with%20Hezbollah.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20think%20there%20is%20a%20realization%2C%20certainly%20in%20the%20international%20community%2C%20that%20a%20full-blown%20war%20between%20Hezbollah%20and%20Israel%20will%20decimate%20Lebanon%20and%20also%20lead%20to%20major%20destruction%20in%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20about%20pressure%20within%20Israel%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECertainly%20within%20Israel%20there%20is%20a%20strong%20lobby%20for%20war%20with%20Hezbollah.%20The%20thinking%20among%20Israeli%20military%20hawks%20here%20is%20a%20powerful%20military%20blow%20against%20Hezbollah%20would%20allow%20people%20living%20in%20the%20north%20of%20Israel%20to%20return%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnn.com%2F2023%2F11%2F20%2Fmiddleeast%2Fisrael-lebanon-hezbollah-tiberias-evacuation-intl%2Findex.html%5C%22%3Ehomes%20they%20evacuated%3C%2Fa%3E%20when%20it%20looked%20like%20war%20might%20be%20in%20the%20cards.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndeed%2C%20the%20Israeli%20Ministry%20of%20Defense%20wanted%20preemptive%20war%20with%20Hezbollah%20after%20the%20Oct.%207%20attack%20by%20Hamas.%20But%20U.S.%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20stopped%20that%20from%20happening%20for%20the%20same%20reason%20that%20Blinken%20is%20currently%20trying%20to%20dissuade%20Israel%20from%20further%20escalating%20the%20conflict.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAnd%20what%20about%20Hezbollah%3F%20How%20might%20it%20respond%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENasrallah%2C%20Hezbollah%E2%80%99s%20leader%2C%20is%20between%20a%20rock%20and%20a%20hard%20place.%20The%20majority%20of%20Lebanese%20people%20clearly%20do%20not%20want%20a%20war.%20But%20any%20attack%20resulting%20in%20the%20deaths%20of%20high-ranking%20Hezbollah%20figures%20will%20be%20met%20by%20internal%20demands%20for%20action.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20there%20is%20a%20tipping%20point%20for%20Hezbollah%2C%20as%20there%20is%20for%20the%20Israelis%20too%20%E2%80%93%20which%20is%20why%20this%20tit-for-tat%20pattern%20is%20such%20a%20risky%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20Lebanese%20side%2C%20if%20Israel%20hits%20strategic%20Hezbollah%20assets%20deep%20in%20Lebanon%20%E2%80%93%20that%20is%2C%20outside%20the%20border%20areas%20%E2%80%93%20or%20launch%20an%20attack%20that%20leads%20to%20mass%20civilian%20deaths%20then%20it%20might%20lead%20to%20full-blown%20conflict.%20But%20so%20far%20that%20has%20not%20been%20the%20case.%20The%20attacks%20by%20Israel%20have%20been%20surgical%20and%20precise.%20In%20the%20case%20of%20the%20Hamas%20leader%20killed%20in%20Beirut%2C%20it%20was%20only%20Palestinians%20killed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20a%20humiliation%20for%20Hezbollah%20for%20sure%20%E2%80%93%20it%20happened%20in%20Hezbollah%E2%80%99s%20stronghold%20in%20southern%20Beirut.%20But%20it%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20on%20Hezbollah%20assets%2C%20such%20as%20personnel%2C%20strategic%20sites%20or%20command%20centers.%20Israel%20has%20limited%20its%20attacks%20largely%20to%20the%20border%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPublic%20sentiment%20is%20still%20very%20strongly%20against%20war%20in%20Lebanon.%20Certainly%20there%20is%20strong%20sympathy%20for%20Gazans.%20But%20the%20prevailing%20sentiment%20in%20Lebanon%20is%20that%20support%20cannot%20come%20at%20the%20price%20of%20Lebanese%20lives.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20that%20suits%20the%20Hezbollah%20hierarchy%20at%20present.%20They%20know%20that%20the%20threat%20of%20war%20is%20their%20most%20important%20card.%20Once%20played%2C%20they%20can%E2%80%99t%20use%20it%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIs%20there%20a%20diplomatic%20way%20forward%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20parties%20are%20looking%20at%20diplomacy.%20Israeli%20Defense%20Minister%20Yoav%20Gallant%20has%20said%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Fnational-security%2F2024%2F01%2F07%2Fisrael-hezbollah-lebanon-blinken%2F%5C%22%3Ehis%20country%E2%80%99s%20preferred%20path%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20%E2%80%9Can%20agreed-upon%20diplomatic%20settlement.%E2%80%9D%20Meanwhile%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.jns.org%2Fnetanyahu-tells-hezbollah-to-learn-from-what-idf-did-to-hamas%2F%5C%22%3Ehas%20said%20the%20goal%20of%20returning%20Israeli%20citizens%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20their%20homes%20in%20the%20north%20would%20be%20done%20%E2%80%9Cdiplomatically%E2%80%9D%20if%20possible.%20But%20added%2C%20%E2%80%9CIf%20not%2C%20we%20will%20work%20in%20other%20ways.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimilarly%20in%20Lebanon%2C%20the%20talk%20is%20of%20a%20diplomatic%20solution%20%E2%80%93%20notably%20by%20enforcing%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpeacemaker.un.org%2Fisraellebanon-resolution1701%5C%22%3EUnited%20Nations%20Resolution%201701%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20calls%20for%20Hezbollah%20to%20withdraw%20north%20of%20the%20Litani%20River%20and%20for%20Israel%20to%20withdraw%20to%20the%20international%20border.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20it%20isn%E2%80%99t%20that%20there%20isn%E2%80%99t%20a%20credible%20diplomatic%20path.%20And%20the%20fact%20that%20both%20sides%20use%20the%20language%20of%20diplomacy%20suggests%20there%20is%20no%20appetite%20for%20full-blown%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndeed%2C%20the%20U.S.%20has%20long%20been%20trying%20to%20get%20Israel%20and%20Lebanon%20to%20resolve%20disputes%20over%20their%20shared%20borders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20sides%20signed%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.state.gov%2Fhistoric-agreement-establishing-a-permanent-israel-lebanon-maritime-boundary%2F%5C%22%3EU.S.-brokered%20maritime%20agreement%20in%202022%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20there%20have%20been%20attempts%20at%20a%20similar%20deal%20in%20regards%20to%20the%20land%20boundary.%20There%20remained%20disagreement%20over%2013%20spots%20along%20the%20border.%20But%20since%20Oct.%207%2C%20the%20U.S.%20has%20tried%20to%20use%20the%20prospect%20of%20a%20negotiated%20land%20solution%20based%20on%20U.N.%20Resolution%201701%20to%20diffuse%20tension%20between%20Israel%20and%20Lebanon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Lebanese%20government%20has%20said%20it%20welcomes%20U.S.%20efforts%20to%20resolve%20the%20disputes.%20On%20the%20Israeli%20side%2C%20too%2C%20they%20are%20going%20along%20with%20U.S.%20attempts%20to%20keep%20U.N.%20Resolution%201701%20on%20the%20table%20%E2%80%93%20I%20think%2C%20mainly%20to%20keep%20America%20on%20side.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDoes%20Iran%20have%20any%20role%20in%20influencing%20Hezbollah%E2%80%99s%20response%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIran%20has%20immense%20influence%20over%20Hezbollah%20%E2%80%93%20it%20pays%20for%20military%20operations%20and%20equipment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20Hezbollah%20is%20not%20only%20an%20Iranian%20proxy%3B%20it%20has%20domestic%20considerations%2C%20and%20its%20interests%20lie%20with%20the%20Lebanese%20political%20scene.%20For%20that%20reason%2C%20Hezbollah%20is%20attuned%20to%20the%20domestic%20popular%20pressure%20in%20Lebanon%20against%20a%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlso%2C%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20think%20Iran%20wants%20to%20see%20an%20escalation.%20Like%20Hezbollah%2C%20Iranian%20leaders%20know%20that%20threat%20of%20war%20%E2%80%93%20through%20their%20proxies%20in%20the%20region%20%E2%80%93%20is%20their%20most%20valuable%20asset.%20And%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20think%20Iran%20is%20ready%20to%20use%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIran%20might%20also%20be%20concerned%20that%20if%20fighting%20escalates%2C%20then%20it%20will%20be%20drawn%20into%20war.%20Iran%20has%20so%20far%20played%20a%20smart%20game%20since%20the%20Oct.%207%20attacks%20%E2%80%93%20it%20has%20stayed%20away%20from%20the%20battlefield%2C%20while%20supporting%20the%20sporadic%20attacks%20on%20Israel%20by%20Hamas%2C%20Hezbollah%2C%20the%20Houthis%20in%20Yemen%20and%20pro-Iranian%20militias%20in%20Iraq%20and%20Syria.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20a%20full%20war%20between%20Israel%20and%20Hezbollah%20may%20draw%20Iran%20into%20direct%20confrontation%20with%20Israel%20and%20the%20U.S.%20And%20that%20is%20something%20that%20leaders%20in%20Tehran%20will%20most%20likely%20not%20want%2C%20especially%20after%20a%20terror%20attack%20in%20Iran%20on%20Jan.%203%20exposed%20how%20vulnerable%20Iran%20is%20internally.%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Conversation%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcounter.theconversation.com%2Fcontent%2F220745%2Fcount.gif%3Fdistributor%3Drepublish-lightbox-basic%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheconversation.com%2Fprofiles%2Fasher-kaufman-1480414%5C%22%3EAsher%20Kaufman%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Professor%20of%20History%20and%20Peace%20Studies%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheconversation.com%2Finstitutions%2Funiversity-of-notre-dame-990%5C%22%3EUniversity%20of%20Notre%20Dame%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20is%20republished%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheconversation.com%5C%22%3EThe%20Conversation%3C%2Fa%3E%20under%20a%20Creative%20Commons%20license.%20Read%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheconversation.com%2Fwhy-both-israel-and-hezbollah-are-eager-to-avoid-tit-for-tat-attacks-escalating-into-full-blown-war-220745%5C%22%3Eoriginal%20article%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704958639000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F02%2F15164743%2Ftaylor-brandon-Y8r0RTNrIWM-unsplash.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fwhy-israel-and-hezbollah-are-eager-to-avoid-a-full-blown-regional-war%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Lebanese%20government%20has%20said%20it%20welcomes%20U.S.%20efforts%20to%20resolve%20the%20disputes.%20On%20the%20Israeli%20side%2C%20too%2C%20they%20are%20going%20along%20with%20U.S.%20attempts%20to%20keep%20U.N.%20Resolution%201701%20on%20the%20table.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fwhy-israel-and-hezbollah-are-eager-to-avoid-a-full-blown-regional-war%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Man%20Finds%20Seat%20Cushion%20Missing%20On%20IndiGo%20Flight%2C%20Airline%20Responds%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20man%20recently%20took%20to%20social%20media%20and%20shared%20his%20harrowing%20experience%20with%20Indigo%20Airlines.%20Revs%2C%20an%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter)%20user%2C%20shared%20a%20picture%20of%20a%20missing%20seat%20cushion%20on%20an%20IndiGo%20flight.%20According%20to%20him%2C%20the%20flight%20was%20already%20delayed%20by%20one%20and%20a%20half%20hours.%20On%20top%20of%20it%2C%20the%20passengers%20were%20made%20to%20wait%20so%20that%20the%20staff%20could%20bring%20seat%20cushions.%20However%2C%20the%20user%20did%20not%20specify%20the%20flight%20number%2C%20route%20or%20seat%20number.%20The%20airlines%20took%20note%20of%20the%20same%20and%20expressed%20regret.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOn%20an%20Indigo%20flight%20and%20the%20flight%20doesn't%20have%20f******%20seats.%20%C2%A0We%20are%20waiting%20for%20them%20to%20bring%20in%20the%20bloody%20seats%20so%20we%20can%20sit.%20This%20for%20a%20flight%20that's%20already%2090%20minutes%20delayed.%20F******%20hell%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FFull_Meals%2Fstatus%2F1745140829700960534%5C%22%3Esaid%20on%20the%20microblogging%20website%3C%2Fa%3E%20along%20with%20a%20picture.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EResponding%20to%20the%20same%2C%20IndiGo%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BHi%2C%20we%20deeply%20regret%20to%20note%20this.%20We%20request%20you%20to%20kindly%20share%20your%20PNR%20via%20DM%20so%20we%20may%20look%20into%20this%20further.%20-Team%20IndiGo%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20being%20shared%2C%20the%20post%20has%20amassed%2031%2C000%20views%20on%20the%20microblogging%20website.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnother%20'strategy'%20to%20get%20the%20passengers%20pay%20for%20the%20actual%20'seat'%3F%20Sorry!%20But%20it%20is%20too%20ridiculous%20%26amp%3B%20funny%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20a%20user.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20user%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BThey%20now%20charge%20extra%20for%20every%20seat%20you%20select.%20Earlier%20it%20was%20only%20for%20window%20seats.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B%40Ryanair%20has%20competition%2C%26quot%3B%20remarked%20a%20person.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIndiGone%20Airlines%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20a%20fourth%20user.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYes%2C%20you%20bought%20a%20flight%20ticket%2C%20but%20did%20you%20'buy'%20a%20seat%3F%20%23Indigo%20has%20anyway%20given%20you%20a%20seatbelt%20for%20free%2C%20And%20you're%20still%20complaining%3F!%26quot%3B%20a%20user%20responds%20sarcastically.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20user%20shared%20his%20experience%20with%20airlines%20and%20stated%2C%20%26quot%3BThis%20reminds%20me%2C%20I%20was%20on%20an%20IndiGo%20flight%20recently%20and%20there%20was%20a%20life%20jacket%20on%20my%20seat.%20I%20checked%20under%20the%20seat%2C%20and%20it%20was%20not%20mine%20so%20told%20the%20cabin%20crew%20and%20they%20put%20it%20in%20the%20overhead%20bin.%20So%20perhaps%20one%20passenger%20didn't%20have%20their%20assigned%20life%20jacket%2C%20for%20the%20flight.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20incident%20comes%20days%20after%20the%20airline%20fixed%20rates%20per%20seat.%20It%20said%20that%20passengers%20will%20have%20to%20pay%20Rs%202%2C000%20for%20front%20row%20seats%20having%20more%20legroom%20in%20budget%20operator%20IndiGo.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20an%20A321%20aircraft%20with%20222%20seats%2C%20selecting%20a%20window%20or%20aisle%20seat%20on%20the%20front%20row%20will%20cost%20Rs%202%2C000.%20It%20is%20Rs%201%2C500%20for%20the%20aisle%20seat%20in%20the%20same%20row.%20For%20the%20second%20and%20third%20rows%2C%20all%20seat%20types%20have%20a%20flat%20rate%20of%20Rs%20400.%20The%20charges%20are%20the%20same%20for%20an%20A321%20plane%20that%20has%20232%20seats%20and%20also%20for%20an%20A320%20aircraft%20with%20180%20seats%2C%20according%20to%20the%20airline's%20website.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704958440000%2C%22visu