duct%20during%20her%20election%20campaign%20in%20Chikmagalur%20in%201978%2C%20pointing%20out%20her%20hypocrisy%20in%20%E2%80%9Cpreaching%20secularism%20in%20between%20visits%20to%20every%20temple%20in%20the%20vicinity.%E2%80%9D%20Religiosity%20in%20the%20public%20square%20was%20then%20frowned%20upon.%20Today%2C%20religion%20has%20not%20only%20become%20integral%20to%20politics%2C%20but%20the%20flaunting%20of%20religious%20fervour%20has%20become%20%3Cem%3Ede%20rigueur%3C%2Fem%3E%20for%20any%20politician%20who%20wants%20to%20%E2%80%98make%20it%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F08%2F07083139%2F2020_8img05_Aug_2020_PTI05-08-2020_000172B.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F08%2F07083139%2F2020_8img05_Aug_2020_PTI05-08-2020_000172B.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F08%2F07083139%2F2020_8img05_Aug_2020_PTI05-08-2020_000172B-300x190.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F08%2F07083139%2F2020_8img05_Aug_2020_PTI05-08-2020_000172B-1024x649.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-471716%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22761%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EPM%20Narendra%20Modi%20takes%20part%20in%20the%20bhoomi%20pujan%20for%20the%20construction%20of%20a%20Ram%20temple%20in%20Ayodhya%2C%20August%205%2C%202020.%20Photo%3A%20PIB%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETo%20reductively%20brush%20off%20the%20buzz%20around%20the%20January%2022%20Ram%20Mandir%20inauguration%20as%20a%20gimmick%20for%20electoral%20purposes%20would%20be%20a%20complete%20misreading%20of%20a%20grim%20situation.%20The%20planned%20mass%20mobilisation%20of%20the%20majority%20community%20%E2%80%93%20the%20running%20of%201%2C000%20trains%20to%20Ayodhya%20from%20various%20parts%20of%20the%20country%2C%20the%20ruling%20party%E2%80%99s%20arrangements%20to%20host%2050%2C000%20pilgrims%20every%20day%2C%20the%20invitation%20to%20150%20disparate%20groups%20cutting%20across%20caste%20lines%C2%A0%20and%204%2C000%C2%A0%20holy%20men%20for%20the%20consecration%20ceremony%2C%20the%20installation%20of%205%20lakh%20LED%20screens%20in%20temples%2C%20the%20prime%20minster%E2%80%99s%20injunction%20to%20celebrate%20January%2022%20as%20Diwali%20by%20lighting%20diyas%20at%20home%20%E2%80%93%20is%20nothing%20less%20than%20a%20carefully%20calibrated%20campaign%20of%20consolidation%20of%20Hindu%20society%20and%20a%20call%20to%20arms%20for%20furthering%20the%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3Ekamandal%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%20project%20whose%20ultimate%20mission%20is%20the%20reclaiming%20of%20temples%2C%20implementation%20of%20the%20uniform%20civil%20code%2C%20ban%20on%20cow%20slaughter%2C%20halal%20meat%2C%20the%20hijab%20and%20a%20lot%20more.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20clear%20subterranean%20text%20is%20not%20difficult%20to%20guess%2C%20which%20is%20the%20%E2%80%9Cothering%E2%80%9D%20of%20minorities%20and%20Muslims%20in%20particular.%20At%20its%20core%2C%20the%20mobilisation%20of%20the%20masses%20(only%20Hindu)%20for%20the%20Ram%20temple%20consecration%20is%20clearly%20intended%20to%20whip%20up%20a%20communal%20consensus%20on%20a%20Hindu%20Rashtra.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Freligion%2Fsanatan-hindu-dharma-highest-guru-ram-temple%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Why%204%20Highest%20Gurus%20of%20Sanatan%20Hindu%20Dharma%20Won%E2%80%99t%20Participate%20in%20Ram%20Temple%20Pranpratistha%2C%E2%80%99%20Explains%20Pro-Hindutva%20Portal%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20are%20disturbing%20markers%20that%20capture%20the%20zeitgeist%20of%20our%20times%20%E2%80%93%20of%20a%20majoritarian%20State%20that%20is%20on%20a%20mission%20to%20reduce%20the%20minorities%20to%20second-class%20citizens.%20The%20Ram%20temple%20is%20not%20quite%20done%20but%20there%20are%20already%20menacing%20rumblings%20around%20the%20Gyanvapi%20masjid%20in%20Varanasi%20and%20the%20Shahi%20Idgah%20mosque%20in%20Mathura.%20We%20know%20by%20now%20that%20the%20slogan%2C%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EYeh%20to%20sirf%20jhanki%20hai%2C%20Kashi-Mathura%20baaki%20hai%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E(This%20is%20just%20a%20trailer%2C%20Kashi%20and%20Mathura%20are%20still%20pending)%E2%80%9D%2C%20is%20no%20idle%20boast!%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOur%20home%20minister%2C%20who%20says%20it%20like%20it%20is%2C%20has%20announced%20to%20the%20world%20that%20the%20Citizens%20Amendment%20Act%20(CAA)%2C%20which%20brazenly%20discriminates%20against%20Muslims%2C%20will%20soon%20be%20implemented.%20As%20ominous%20is%20his%20calculated%20statement%20that%20Modi%20had%20cured%20Gujarat%20of%20riots%20by%20teaching%20rioters%20(read%20Muslims)%20a%20lesson%20in%202002.%20By%20obliquely%20suggesting%20that%20Modi%20had%20presided%20over%20the%20nightmarish%20events%20in%20the%20aftermath%20of%20the%20Godhra%20train%20burning%2C%20the%20home%20minister%20is%20thumbing%20a%20nose%20at%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20verdict%20exonerating%20Modi%20of%20any%20involvement%20in%20the%20genocide%20that%20followed%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20Godhra.%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20closest%20aide%20has%20made%20this%20provocative%20claim%20because%20he%20knows%20that%20for%20millions%20of%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20followers%2C%20the%20undying%20faith%20in%20Modi%20stems%20primarily%20from%20their%20fond%20belief%20that%20he%20is%20the%20only%20leader%20who%20can%20deal%20effectively%20with%20the%20%E2%80%9CMuslim%20menace.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOf%20a%20piece%20with%20the%20planned%2C%20all-out%20offensive%20against%20Muslims%20is%20the%20obnoxious%2C%20dastardly%20attack%20on%20the%20Muslim%20community%20by%20BJP%20MP%20Ramesh%20Bidhuri%20from%20within%20the%20sacred%20precincts%20of%20Parliament%20even%20as%20senior%20BJP%20members%20beamed%20with%20delight.%20No%20action%20was%20taken%20against%20him.%20In%20a%20hate-filled%20environment%20that%20thrives%20on%20Muslim%20bashing%2C%20this%20hate-monger%20could%20well%20be%20the%20new%20poster%20boy%20of%20the%20BJP%20like%20Yogi%20Adityanath%20and%20Sadhvi%20Pragya%20before%20him.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Freligion%2Fsanatan-strikes-back-how-dare-modi-perform-the-consecration-ceremony-asks-a-priest%5C%22%3ESanatan%20Strikes%20Back%3A%20%E2%80%98How%20Dare%20Modi%20Perform%20the%20Consecration%20Ceremony%2C%E2%80%99%20Asks%20a%20Priest%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20present%20regime%20has%20smashed%20the%20flimsy%20secular%20facade%20that%20corralled%20the%20state%20from%20religion%2C%20which%20is%20now%20front%20and%20centre%20in%20the%20public%20arena%20and%20the%20ultimate%20arbiter%20of%20temporal%20power.%20The%20savage%20conduct%20of%20the%20%3Cem%3Etrishul%3C%2Fem%3E-brandishing%20%3Cem%3Ebhakts%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%20recent%20years%20under%20the%20benign%20gaze%20of%20the%20state%2C%20vindicates%20Italian%20philosopher%20Umberto%20Eco%E2%80%99s%20observation%20that%20ordinary%20people%20are%20never%20so%20completely%20and%20enthusiastically%20evil%20as%20when%20they%20act%20out%20of%20religious%20conviction.%20The%20collective%20delirium%20over%20the%20consecration%20of%20the%20Ram%20temple%20at%20Ayodhya%20under%20the%20aegis%20of%20the%20Modi%20government%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0represents%20the%20emphatic%20triumph%20of%20religious%20fundamentalism%20over%20secularism%2C%20of%20Hindutva%20over%20Hinduism%2C%20of%20religiosity%20over%20religion%2C%20of%20exclusion%20over%20inclusion%2C%20of%20hate%20over%20brotherhood.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERam%20must%20be%20distraught%2C%20if%20not%20enraged%2C%20at%20what%20is%20being%20done%20in%20his%20name.%20He%20is%20the%20epitome%20of%20justice%2C%20compassion%2C%20peace%20and%20non-violence.%20He%20personifies%20truthfulness%2C%20forgiveness%2C%20accountability%20and%20empathy%20with%20his%20subjects.%20From%20the%20%3Cem%3ERamayana%3C%2Fem%3E%20we%20know%20that%20Ram%20was%20the%20perfect%20son%2C%20the%20ideal%20husband%20and%20the%20quintessentially%20responsible%20ruler.%20As%20depicted%20in%20the%20%3Cem%3ERamayana%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Ram%E2%80%99s%20story%20in%20essence%20embodies%20the%20victory%20of%20righteousness%20over%20evil%20and%20the%20advent%20of%20Ram%20Rajya.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20greatest%20Indian%20and%20Hindu%2C%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%20who%20was%20deeply%20influenced%20by%20the%20%3Cem%3ERamayana%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20in%20an%20expository%20piece%20that%20appeared%20in%20%3Cem%3EYoung%20Indian%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%201929%2C%20explained%20what%20Ram%20Rajya%20means%3A%20%E2%80%9CBy%20Ram%20Rajya%2C%20I%20do%20not%20mean%20Hindu%20Raj.%20I%20mean%20Ram%20Raj%2C%20the%20kingdom%20of%20God.%20For%20me%20Ram%20and%20Rahim%20are%20one%20and%20the%20same%3B%20I%20acknowledge%20no%20other%20God%20but%20the%20one%20God%20of%20truth%20and%20righteousness.%E2%80%9D%20For%20the%20Mahatma%2C%20Ram%20Rajya%20meant%20equal%20citizenship%20%E2%80%93%20%E2%80%9Cequal%20rights%20to%20both%20prince%20and%20pauper.%E2%80%9D%20Is%20it%20any%20surprise%20then%20that%20Gandhism%20is%20viewed%20as%20a%20mortal%20enemy%20of%20Hindutva%3F%20But%20by%20the%20looks%20of%20it%2C%20Hindutva%20is%20up%20and%20running%20and%20to%20hell%20with%20Gandhiji%20and%20secularism.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20grand%20consecration%20on%20January%2022%20is%20slated%20to%20be%20the%20greatest%20politico-religious%20event%20of%20our%20time%20and%20will%20be%20presided%20over%20by%20the%20high%20priest%20of%20Hindutva%2C%20the%20prime%20minister%20himself.%20But%20far%20from%20being%20the%20crowning%20glory%20of%20a%20great%20religion%2C%20the%20Ram%20Mandir%2C%20built%20on%20the%20ruins%20of%20a%20mosque%20vandalised%20by%20religious%20fanatics%20and%20now%20in%20the%20hands%20of%20the%20vandals%20and%20their%20mentors%20is%2C%20in%20truth%2C%20a%20symbol%20of%20the%20triumph%20of%20majoritarian%20nationalism.%20As%20an%20outlier%20who%20has%20watched%20with%20cold%20fear%20the%20march%20of%20Hindutva%20to%20the%20centre%20of%20our%20national%20life%2C%20the%20Ram%20temple%20symbolises%20the%20formal%20investiture%20of%20the%20Hindu%20Rashtra%20and%20the%20death%20of%20secular%20India.%20One%20wonders%20what%20our%20founding%20fathers%20would%20have%20thought%20of%20such%20a%20radical%20transmutation%20of%20the%20body%20politic.%C2%A0%20Their%20angst%20can%20best%20be%20expressed%20by%20invoking%20Mahatma%E2%80%99s%20last%20anguished%20cry%3A%20%E2%80%9CHey%20Ram!%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EMathew%20John%20is%20a%20former%20civil%20servant.%20The%20views%20are%20personal.%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704957345000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F11121926%2FScreenshot-2024-01-11-at-12.18.29-PM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fdelirium-over-ram-mandir-a-nation-consecrated-or-desecrated%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20collective%20hullaballoo%20over%20the%20consecration%20of%20the%20Ram%20temple%20under%20the%20aegis%20of%20the%20Modi%20government%C2%A0represents%20the%20triumph%20of%20religious%20fundamentalism%20over%20secularism.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fdelirium-over-ram-mandir-a-nation-consecrated-or-desecrated%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Cactos%20builds%20energy%20storage%20systems%20with%20old%20Tesla%20batteries.%20It%20just%20raised%20%2428.5%20million%20with%20this%2024-slide%20pitch%20deck.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222048%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Cactos%20team%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F659c0226ec62ab5daf817468%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221638%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Cactos%20team%20stand%20alongside%20battery%20storage%20units.%3Cp%3ECactos%2FMikko-Pekka%20Karlin%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EFinnish%20energy%20storage%20startup%20has%20raised%C2%A026%20million%20euros%20(%2428.5%20million)%20in%20fresh%20funds.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20cash%20is%20part%20of%20a%20separate%20fund%20that%20will%20be%20used%20to%20finance%20the%20roll-out%20of%20the%20batteries.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ECheck%20out%20the%2024-slide%20pitch%20deck%20it%20used%20to%20raise%20the%20capital%20below.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EA%20Finnish%20startup%20that%20uses%20both%20recycled%20Tesla%20batteries%20and%20new%20batteries%20to%20build%20energy%20storage%20systems%20has%20raised%2026%20million%20euros%2C%20%2428.5%20million%2C%20in%20fresh%20funds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECactos%2C%20which%20was%20founded%20in%202021%2C%20has%20developed%20storage%20systems%20that%20enable%20companies%20operating%20in%20areas%20like%20real%20estate%20and%20logistics%20to%20buy%20energy%20when%20it's%20cheap%20and%20plentiful%2C%20store%20it%2C%20and%20use%20it%20later.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOskari%20Jaakkola%2C%20the%20startup's%20chief%20executive%2C%20said%20the%20electricity%20market%20recorded%20%26quot%3B1%2C000-fold%20intraday%20price%20fluctuations.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20obviously%20gives%20a%20very%20good%20background%20for%20storage%2C%20because%20you%20know%20the%20prices%20upfront%2C%26quot%3B%20Jaakkola%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou're%20going%20to%20be%20able%20to%20buy%20cheap%20and%20sell%20expensive.%20So%20that's%20really%20where%20the%20idea%20came%20from%2C%20from%20the%20markets.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECase%20in%20point%3A%20Energy%20prices%20were%20at%20an%20all-time%20high%20in%20Finland%20on%20January%205.%20A%20lack%20of%20wind%20and%20long%2C%20cold%20stints%20have%20meant%20that%20energy%20production%20is%20lower%2C%20but%20demand%20is%20higher%2C%20meaning%20people%20pay%20more%2C%20Jaakkola%20said.%20The%20country%20has%20also%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fbusiness%2Fenergy%2Ffinnish-power-supply-stable-amid-cold-weather-record-price-2024-01-05%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eramped%20up%20gas%20imports%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20a%20result.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECactos%20owns%2C%20operates%2C%20and%20finances%20the%20battery%20storage%20units%20for%20customers%2C%20who%20take%20on%2010-year%20leases%20for%20a%20monthly%20fee.%20The%20units%20can%20be%20used%20to%20power%20buildings%20or%20charge%20a%20large%20fleet%20of%20electric%20vehicles%2C%20for%20example.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20means%20customers%20with%20high%20energy%20demands%20can%20avoid%20price%20volatility%20and%20make%20money%20by%20selling%20energy%20back%20to%20the%20grid%20at%20a%20profit.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBatteries%20also%20offer%20backup%20power%20in%20the%20event%20of%20an%20outage%20and%20can%20help%20optimize%20the%20use%20of%20home%20power%20generation%2C%20the%20company%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECactos%20raised%20funds%20in%20a%20manner%20similar%20to%20that%20of%20an%20investment%20fund%2C%20splitting%20its%20more%20stable%2C%20long-term%20leasing%20of%20assets%20business%20from%20its%20more%20high-risk%20technology%20play.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe've%20developed%20our%20technologies%20ourselves%20and%2C%20in%20that%20sense%2C%20that%20part%20of%20the%20company%20is%20quite%20a%20traditional%20startup%2C%26quot%3B%20Jaakkola%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BObviously%2C%20that's%20a%20venture%20capital%20play%20and%20venture%20capital%20funding%20is%20expensive.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJaakkola%20said%20the%20company's%20%26quot%3Bsecond%20line%20of%20business%26quot%3B%20was%20its%20leasing%20of%20storage%20systems.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20very%20stable%20business%20with%20a%20very%20high%20degree%20of%20fixed%20cash%20flows%2C%20long-term%20cash%20flows%20from%20our%20contracts%20which%20are%2010%20years%20fixed.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20splitting%20the%20two%2C%20the%20energy%20system%20roll-out%20can%20be%20funded%20with%20a%20%26quot%3Bconsiderably%20lower%20cost%20of%20capital%26quot%3B%20as%20a%20typical%20infrastructure%20investment%2C%20Jaakkola%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20cash%20injection%20is%20Cactos'%20first%20close%20on%20its%20Cactos%20Fleet%20Finland%20Limited%20Partnership%20fund%2C%20with%2026%20million%20euros%20in%20equity%20coming%20from%20OP%20Finland%20Infrastructure%20LP%20and%20the%20Finnish%20Climate%20Fund.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECactos%20aims%20to%20raise%2035%20million%20euros%20in%20equity%20and%2035%20million%20euros%20in%20debt%20in%20total.%20It%20will%20spend%20the%20cash%20%E2%80%93%20buying%20energy%20storage%20systems%20from%20Cactos%20%E2%80%93%20over%20two%20and%20a%20half%20years.%20The%20fund%20will%20be%20operational%20for%20around%2010%20years%2C%20akin%20to%20a%20typical%20VC%20fund%20lifecycle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECactos%20finds%20the%20clients%2C%20signs%20a%20leasing%20contract%20with%20them%2C%20and%20finances%20the%20working%20capital%20during%20the%20construction%20of%20the%20system.%20Once%20the%20system%20is%20installed%2C%20it%20is%20sold%20to%20the%20fund%20along%20with%20the%20leasing%20contract%2C%20so%20Cactos%20gets%20paid%20at%20the%20point%20of%20sale%2C%20and%20the%20fund%20receives%20the%20recurring%20revenue.%20The%20hardware%2C%20then%20owned%20by%20the%20fund%2C%20is%20managed%20via%20Cactos'%20software%20platform.%3C%2F