ost%20eligible%20bachelors%2C%20is%20set%20to%20marry%20his%20commoner%20fiancee%20on%20Thursday%20as%20part%20of%20a%20lavish%2010-day%20celebration%20in%20the%20oil-rich%20sultanate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20Islamic%20marriage%20ceremony%20for%20the%2032-year-old%20prince%20and%20Yang%20Mulia%20Anisha%20Rosnah%2C%2029%2C%20will%20be%20held%20inside%20a%20gold-domed%20mosque%20in%20the%20capital%20Bandar%20Seri%20Begawan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMateen%20is%20the%2010th%20child%20of%20Sultan%20Hassanal%20Bolkiah%20--%20the%20world's%20longest%20reigning%20monarch%20and%20once%20the%20richest%20man%20on%20the%20planet%20--%20and%20is%20well%20down%20the%20succession%20pecking%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20bride%20--%20the%20granddaughter%20of%20one%20of%20his%20father's%20key%20advisers%20--%20reportedly%20has%20a%20fashion%20brand%20and%20co-owns%20a%20tourism%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECelebrations%20for%20the%20royal%20wedding%20reach%20their%20climax%20on%20Sunday%20with%20a%20glittering%20ceremony%20in%20the%201%2C788-room%20palace%20and%20an%20elaborate%20procession.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20guest%20list%20is%20expected%20to%20include%20international%20royalty%20and%20political%20leaders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20like%20a%20fairytale%2C%26quot%3B%20university%20student%20Syahida%20Wafa%20Mohamed%20Shah%2C%2022%2C%20told%20AFP%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20near%20the%20Omar%20Ali%20Saifuddien%20Mosque%2C%20where%20the%20marriage%20will%20be%20solemnised.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20Bruneians%20plan%20to%20line%20the%20streets%20for%20Sunday's%20procession%20when%20the%20couple%20will%20pass%20by%20in%20a%20royal%20carriage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20like%20something%20from%20a%20movie%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Nazatul%20Izzati%20Saifulrizal%2C%2019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EExtreme%20wealth%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20pomp%20and%20pageantry%20of%20the%20royal%20extravaganza%20highlights%20the%20tiny%20country's%20extreme%20wealth%2C%20which%20is%20almost%20entirely%20derived%20from%20its%20enormous%20oil%20reserves.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20sliver%20of%20land%20on%20the%20northern%20edge%20of%20Borneo%20island%20in%20Southeast%20Asia%2C%20Brunei%20was%20influenced%20by%20Buddhism%20and%20Hinduism%20before%20its%20rulers%20converted%20to%20Islam%20in%20the%2014th%20century.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20fell%20under%20British%20rule%20in%20the%2019th%20century%20and%20gained%20independence%20in%201984.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20absolute%20monarchy%20with%20strict%20Islamic%20laws%20and%20a%20population%20of%20only%20around%20450%2C000%20people%2C%20Brunei%20is%20one%20of%20the%20world's%20richest%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIts%20annual%20GDP%20per%20capita%20is%20nearly%20%2436%2C000%2C%20according%20to%20the%20International%20Monetary%20Fund.%20However%2C%20analysts%20have%20warned%20that%20Brunei%20faces%20serious%20challenges%20to%20diversify%20its%20economy%20away%20from%20oil%20as%20crude%20prices%20remain%20volatile%20and%20its%20reserves%20dwindle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20sultan%20has%20long%20lost%20the%20title%20of%20the%20world's%20richest%20man%20to%20tech%20billionaires%2C%20his%20wealth%20remains%20the%20stuff%20of%20legend.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20is%20reported%20to%20have%20a%20vast%20collection%20of%20luxury%20vehicles%20and%20his%20riverside%20official%20residence%20is%20one%20of%20the%20world's%20largest%20palaces.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Hot%20royal'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Mateen%20is%20unlikely%20to%20ever%20ascend%20the%20throne%2C%20his%20matinee%20idol%20looks%20and%20huge%20following%20on%20social%20media%20have%20made%20him%20one%20of%20the%20highest-profile%20members%20of%20the%20royal%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20helicopter%20pilot%20in%20his%20country's%20air%20force%2C%20he%20has%20often%20been%20compared%20in%20the%20media%20with%20Britain's%20Prince%20Harry%20and%20was%20previously%20dubbed%20the%20%26quot%3Bhot%