E2%80%99%20in%20the%20murder%20case%20of%20Samajwadi%20Party%20youth%20leader%20Prabhat%20Gupta%20in%202000.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETeni%2C%20the%20member%20of%20parliament%20from%20Lakhimpur%20Kheri%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20holds%20the%20Union%20minister%20of%20state%20for%20home%20affairs%20portfolio%20in%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Monday%20(January%208)%2C%20a%20division%20bench%20of%20Justices%20Bela%20M.%20Trivedi%20and%20Pankaj%20Mithal%20dismissed%20a%20special%20leave%20petition%20(SLP)%20filed%20by%20the%20deceased%E2%80%99s%20brother%2C%20Rajeev%20Gupta%2C%20against%20the%20high%20court%20judgment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESenior%20counsel%20Kapil%20Sibal%20appeared%20for%20Gupta.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20bench%20said%20that%20after%20having%20heard%20Sibal%20%E2%80%9Cat%20length%20and%20after%20carefully%20perusing%20the%20material%20placed%20on%20record%2C%20we%20are%20not%20inclined%20to%20interfere%20with%20the%20concurrent%20findings%20of%20facts%20recorded%20by%20the%20two%20Courts.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20UP%20government%20did%20not%20file%20an%20SLP%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20challenging%20the%20high%20court%E2%80%99s%20judgement%20despite%20Gupta%E2%80%99s%20requests%2C%20he%20approached%20the%20top%20court%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20May%2019%2C%202023%2C%20the%20high%20court%20upheld%20the%20acquittal%20of%20Teni%20and%20three%20others%20in%20the%2023-year-old%20murder%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20dismissed%20the%20criminal%20appeal%20and%20revision%20appeal%20filed%20against%20their%20acquittal%20by%20a%20sessions%20court%20in%20Lakhimpur%20Kheri%20in%202004.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20upholding%20the%20trial%20court%20verdict%2C%20the%20high%20court%20said%20the%20%E2%80%9Cprosecution%20has%20utterly%20failed%20to%20establish%20the%20chain%20of%20events%20which%20can%20be%20said%20to%20exclusively%20lead%20to%20the%20one%20and%20only%20conclusion%2C%20i.e.%2C%20the%20guilt%20of%20the%20accused%20persons.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fajay-mishra-2000-murder-case-lakhimpur-kheri%5C%22%3EWho%20Was%20Ajay%20Mishra%20Before%20He%20Became%20a%20Legislator%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20division%20bench%20of%20Justices%20Attau%20Rahman%20Masoodi%20and%20Om%20Prakash%20Shukla%20noted%20that%20the%20%E2%80%9Cevidence%20recorded%20in%20the%20present%20case%20has%20been%20appreciated%20in%20its%20correct%20perspective%20and%20the%20trial%20court%20has%20at%20no%20point%20of%20time%20missed%20the%20woods%20of%20the%20tree.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20court%20has%20also%20recorded%20its%20independent%20finding%20and%20holds%20that%20the%20theory%20put%20forth%20by%20prosecution%20that%20the%20four%20accused%20persons%20were%20liable%20for%20causing%20death%20of%20the%20deceased%20is%20unconvincing%20and%20shorn%20of%20evidence%20proved%20beyond%20reasonable%20doubt%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20the%20high%20court%20bench.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERajeev%20Gupta%2C%20who%20has%20fought%20a%20long%20battle%20to%20get%20justice%20for%20his%20brother%2C%20was%20again%20left%20disappointed%20after%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20dismissed%20his%20SLP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20the%20highest%20authority%20in%20the%20country%2C%20the%20SC%2C%20will%20not%20interfere%2C%20then%20where%20will%20people%20like%20us%20go%20for%20justice%3F%20Where%20will%20the%20victims%20go%3F%E2%80%9D%20Gupta%20asked%20while%20speaking%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESC%20bench%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20December%206%2C%202023%2C%20the%20advocate%20on%20record%20for%20the%20petitioner%2C%20Pragya%20Baghel%2C%20had%20written%20to%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20Registrar%20(Listing)%20requesting%20it%20to%20pass%20%E2%80%9Cappropriate%20orders%E2%80%9D%20so%20that%20the%20matter%20could%20be%20heard%20on%20the%20next%20day%20of%20listing%20before%20the%20bench%20presided%20by%20Justice%20Aniruddha%20Bose.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20the%20rules%20framed%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20the%20matter%20should%20have%20been%20listed%20before%20Justice%20Bose%2C%20said%20Baghel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20matter%20was%2C%20however%2C%20heard%20by%20Justices%20Trivedi%20and%20Mithal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20murder%20case%20dates%20back%20to%202000%2C%20when%20Teni%2C%20today%20a%20prominent%20and%20controversial%20minister%20in%20the%20NDA%20government%2C%20was%20a%20BJP%20worker%20in%20the%20Terai%20district%20of%20Lakhimpur%20Kheri%20and%20was%20yet%20to%20enter%20state-level%20electoral%20politics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20FIR%2C%20Prabhat%20Gupta%20and%20Teni%20had%20a%20rivalry%20over%20panchayat%20elections%20and%20on%20July%208%2C%202000%2C%20when%20Prabhat%20Gupta%20was%20going%20to%20his%20shop%20from%20his%20house%2C%20he%20was%20shot%20at%20on%20his%20temple%20and%20between%20his%20chest%20and%20abdomen.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FfSO4X6rzVXg%3Ffeature%3Doembed%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Lakhimpur%20Kheri%20Case%3A%20Ajay%20Mishra%20Teni%20Slams%20Reporters%20When%20Asked%20About%20the%20SIT%20Report%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22473%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20fell%20on%20the%20ground%20and%20died%2C%20said%20the%20revision%20petition%20filed%20by%20his%20father%2C%20Santosh%20Gupta%20(now%20deceased)%2C%20in%20the%20high%20court%20in%202004%20following%20the%20trial%20court%20acquittal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETeni%20and%20three%20of%20his%20associates%20were%20accused%20of%20the%20crime.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20accused%20told%20the%20court%20they%20had%20been%20falsely%20implicated%20due%20to%20political%20rivalry%20and%20enmity%20over%20the%20panchayat%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20legal%20battle%20in%20the%20high%20court%20was%20a%20long-drawn%20affair%20marked%20by%20adjournments%20and%20judicial%20delays.%20It%20took%20almost%20two%20decades%20for%20a%20judgement%20to%20finally%20be%20pronounced%20against%20the%20trial%20court%20verdict%20of%202004.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20May%2019%20last%20year%2C%20the%20high%20court%20dismissed%20the%20government%20appeal%20filed%20by%20the%20state%20of%20UP%20and%20the%20revision%20appeal%20filed%20by%20Prabhat%20Gupta%E2%80%99s%20father.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Prabhat%20Gupta%20murder%20case%20had%20been%20long%20forgotten%2C%20until%20Teni%20got%20engulfed%20by%20the%20incident%20of%20the%20mowing%20down%20of%20farmers%20by%20a%20convoy%20of%20cars%20linked%20to%20him%20on%20October%203%2C%202021%20in%20Lakhimpur%20Kheri.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20sprung%20into%20the%20spotlight%20for%20the%20wrong%20reasons%20after%20his%20son%20Ashish%20Mishra%20alias%20Monu%20and%20his%20associates%20were%20accused%20of%20murdering%20four%20farmers%20in%20Tikonia%20by%20mowing%20them%20down%20under%20their%20SUVs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20total%20of%20eight%20persons%20were%20killed%20in%20the%20incident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThree%20BJP%20workers%2C%20including%20a%20driver%2C%20who%20were%20caught%20by%20the%20enraged%20mob%20of%20protesting%20farmers%20were%20killed%20in%20retaliation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20local%20scribe%2C%20Raman%20Kashyap%2C%20there%20to%20cover%20a%20farmers%E2%80%99%20protest%20against%20controversial%20statements%20made%20by%20Teni%2C%20was%20also%20mowed%20to%20death%20by%20the%20SUVs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fajay-mishra-jailed-farmers-demands-agitation-lakhimpur%5C%22%3E%20%E2%80%98Sack%20Ajay%20Mishra%3B%20Release%20Jailed%20Farmers%E2%80%99%3A%20Demands%20That%20Echoed%20the%2075-Hour%20Agitation%20in%20Lakhimpur%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Teni%E2%80%99s%20son%20Monu%20was%20the%20prime%20accused%20in%20the