0attended%20the%20India-UK%20Defence%20Industry%20CEOs%20Roundtable%20at%20Trinity%20House%20in%20London%2C%26quot%3B%20read%20a%20post%20on%20the%20Defence%20Minister's%20official%20handle%20on%20'X'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20UK%20announced%20its%20plans%20to%20send%20its%20Littoral%20Response%20Group%20to%20the%20Indian%20Ocean%20Region%20later%20this%20year%2C%20with%20a%20proposal%20for%20the%20Carrier%20Strike%20Group%20to%20visit%20the%20Indian%20waters%20in%202025.%20Both%20will%20operate%20and%20train%20with%20Indian%20forces.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20announcement%20was%20made%20by%20UK%20Defence%20Secretary%20Shapps.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20UK%20and%20India%20also%20vowed%20to%20continue%20strengthening%20ties%20during%20Defence%20Minister%20visit%20to%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20move%20that%20signals%20the%20growing%20importance%20of%20the%20strategic%20relationship%20between%20the%20UK%20and%20India%2C%20Defence%20Secretary%20Shapps%20welcomed%20Singh%20to%20the%20UK%20and%20the%20two%20leaders%20agreed%20on%20unprecedented%20levels%20of%20UK-India%20defence%20cooperation%2C%20according%20to%20an%20official%20release.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20nations%20also%20discussed%20future%20cooperation%20in%20defence%20from%20joint%20exercises%20to%20knowledge%20sharing%20and%20instructor%20exchanges.%20These%20steps%20build%20on%20the%20comprehensive%20strategic%20partnership%20envisaged%20in%20the%202030%20India-UK%20roadmap%2C%20announced%20in%202021%2C%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20coming%20years%2C%20the%20UK%20and%20India%20will%20also%20embark%20on%20more%20complex%20exercises%20between%20their%20respective%20militaries%2C%20building%20up%20to%20a%20landmark%20joint%20exercise%20to%20be%20conducted%20before%20the%20end%20of%202030%2C%20supporting%20shared%20goals%20of%20protecting%20critical%20trade%20routes%20and%20upholding%20the%20international%20rules-based%20system%2C%20as%20per%20the%20release.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDefence%20Secretary%20Shapps%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThere%20is%20absolutely%20no%20question%20that%20the%20world%20is%20becoming%20increasingly%20contested%2C%20so%20it's%20vital%20that%20we%20continue%20to%20build%20on%20our%20strategic%20relationships%20with%20key%20partners%20like%20India.%20Together%20we%20share%20the%20same%20security%20challenges%20and%20are%20steadfast%20on%20our%20commitment%20to%20maintaining%20a%20free%20and%20prosperous%20Indo-Pacific.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20it%20is%20clear%20that%20%26quot%3Bthis%20relationship%20is%20going%20from%20strength-to-strength%2C%20but%20we%20must%20continue%20to%20work%20hand-in-hand%20to%20uphold%20global%20security%20in%20light%20of%20threats%20and%20challenges%20that%20seek%20to%20destabilise%20and%20damage%20us%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCollaboration%20with%20industry%20is%20also%20key%20in%20the%20strategic%20defence%20partnership%20between%20the%20UK%20and%20India%2C%20with%20the%20two%20nations%20working%20together%20on%20electric%20propulsion%20systems%20that%20will%20power%20our%20future%20fleets%20and%20cooperating%20on%20the%20development%20of%20complex%20weapons%2C%26quot%3B%20Shapps%20was%20quoted%20as%20saying%20further%20in%20the%20release.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20UK%20and%20India%20also%20confirmed%20several%20new%20joint%20initiatives.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20include%20a%20Letter%20of%20Arrangement%20that%20will%20enable%20further%20emphasis%20to%20be%20placed%20on%20research%20and%20development%20between%20the%20two%20nations%2C%20focused%20on%20next-generation%20capabilities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20also%20include%20solidifying%20an%20agreement%20on%20logistics%20exchange%2C%20allowing%20for%20the%20provision%20of%20logistic%20support%2C%20supplies%20and%20services%20between%20the%20United%20Kingdom%20and%20Indian%20Armed%20Forces%2C%20for%20joint%20training%2C%20joint%20exercises%2C%20authorised%20port%20visits%20and%20Humanitarian%20Assistance%20and%20Disaster%20Relief%20(HADR)%20operations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEearlier%2C%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20Defence%20Minister%20Singh%20on%20Tuesday%20said%20both%20India%20and%20the%20UK%20desire%20strong%20strategic%20relations%20and%20are%20working%20towards%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBoth%20India%20and%20the%20UK%20want%20strong%20strategic%20relations.%20We%20want%20to%20strengthen%20the%20comprehensive%20strategic%20relations%2C%26quot%3B%20Singh%2C%20who%20is%20currently%20on%20an%20official%20visit%20to%20the%20UK%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlso%2C%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20the%20Raksha%20Mantri%20paid%20a%20visit%20to%20the%20BAPS%20Swaminarayan%20Temple%20(Neasden%20Temple)%20in%20London.%20The%20Hindu%20temple%20is%20Europe's%20first%20authentic%20and%20traditionally%20built%20Hindu%20shrine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Singh%20offered%20Abishek%20Puja%20at%20the%20temple%2C%20according%20to%20sources.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Singh's%20visit%20to%20the%20Neasden%20Temple%20also%20underlined%20the%20significance%20of%20cultural%20connections%20in%20bilateral%20relations%20between%20the%20two%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(This%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20auto-generated%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704943560000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2F5hlkbsj4_rajnath-singh-rishi-sunak-twitter_625x300_11_January_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdefence-minister-rajnath-singh-meets-uk-pm-rishi-sunak-in-london-4839343%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Union%20Defence%20Minister%20Rajnath%20Singh%20called%20on%20UK%20Prime%20Minister%20Rishi%20Sunak%20in%20London%20on%20Wednesday.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdefence-minister-rajnath-singh-meets-uk-pm-rishi-sunak-in-london-4839343%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndt