hal%2C%20surrendered%20in%20a%20local%20court%2C%20the%20police%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAhmad%20completed%20his%20graduation%20in%20psychology%20from%20the%20AMU%20in%202022%20and%20had%20appeared%20in%20an%20MBA%20entrance%20examination%20last%20year.%20Malik%20is%20pursuing%20a%20Master%20in%20Social%20Works%20degree%20at%20the%20central%20university.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20UP%20ATS%20alleged%20that%20the%20two%20men%2C%20along%20with%20the%20previously%20arrested%20seven%20persons%20in%20the%20case%2C%20were%20preparing%20an%20ISIS%20module%20in%20AMU%20and%20recruiting%20others%20for%20it.%20All%20the%20arrested%20men%20had%20taken%20the%20%E2%80%9Cbayath%E2%80%9D%C2%A0or%20oath%20of%20allegiance%20to%20the%20ISIS%20and%20were%20deeply%20inspired%20by%20the%20outfit%2C%20the%20police%20claimed.%20The%20arrested%20youth%20were%20linked%20to%20the%20SAMU%20(Students%20of%20Aligarh%20Muslim%20University)%2C%20an%20informal%20student%20body%20on%20campus.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20crackdown%20in%20Aligarh%20started%20with%20the%20arrest%20of%20two%20former%20AMU%20students%20Abdullah%20Arsalan%20and%20Maaz%20Bin%20Tariq%20on%20November%205.%C2%A0%20Two%20days%20later%2C%20the%20UP%20ATS%20arrested%20a%20third%20person%2C%20Wazihuddin%2C%20who%20had%20completed%20his%20PhD%20from%20AMU%2C%20from%20Durg%20in%20Chhattisgarh.%20According%20to%20an%20AMU%20student%2C%20Wazihuddin%20headed%20the%20SAMU.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20UP%20ATS%20said%20it%20recovered%20%E2%80%9Cprinted%20literature%E2%80%9D%20of%20ISIS%20and%20AQIS%20(Al%20Qaeda%20Indian%20Subcontinent)%20and%20a%20pendrive%20with%20ISIS%20propaganda%20from%20the%20arrested%20persons.%20Memory%20card%20of%20their%20electronic%20devices%20showed%20exchange%20of%20%E2%80%9Cbanned%20literature%E2%80%9D%20of%20AQIS%20and%20ISIS%20and%20information%20regarding%20several%20groups%20supporting%20terrorism%20and%20%E2%80%9Canti-national%E2%80%9D%20ideology%2C%20the%20ATS%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20November%2011%2C%202023%2C%20the%20ATS%20arrested%20four%20others%20as%20part%20of%20its%20investigation%20of%20the%20%E2%80%9CAligarh%20Module%20of%20ISIS.%E2%80%9D%20Those%20arrested%20were%20identified%20as%20Raqib%20Imam%2C%2029%2C%20who%20completed%20M.Tech%20from%20AMU%3B%20Naved%20Siddiqui%2C%2023%2C%20who%20is%20studying%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fb.sc%2F%5C%22%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttp%3A%2F%2FB.SC%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1704937745236000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVaw3rtdq2te7fz6_74LqsJ5pU%5C%22%3EB.SC%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0in%20AMU%3B%20Mohammad%20Noman%2C%2027%2C%20who%20completed%20B.A%20Honours%20from%20the%20university%20and%20Mohammad%20Nazim%2C%2033%2C%20who%20police%20said%2C%20was%20linked%20to%20the%20%E2%80%9CISIS%20module%20of%20AMU%E2%80%9D%20through%20Noman.%20Noman%2C%20Nazim%20and%20Siddiqui%20were%20arrested%20from%20their%20native%20Sambhal%20district%20while%20Imam%20was%20arrested%20in%20Aligarh%2C%20said%20police.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20arrested%20persons%20were%20planning%20to%20overthrow%20the%20government%20through%20a%20%E2%80%9Cviolent%20jihad%2C%E2%80%9D%20and%20impose%20Sharia%20law%2C%20the%20ATS%20claimed.%C2%A0%20The%20police%20also%20said%20that%20the%20four%20were%20allegedly%20distributing%20ISIS%20literature%20among%20%E2%80%9Clike-minded%20people%E2%80%9D%20and%20recruiting%20them%20to%20join%20the%20outfit.%20They%20had%20come%20in%20touch%20with%20each%20other%20through%20meetings%20of%20SAMU%20and%20were%20using%20online%20platforms%20and%20physical%20meetings%20to%20physically%20and%20mentally%20train%20people%20at%20%E2%80%9Csecret%20locations%E2%80%9D%20for%20jihad%2C%20the%20ATS%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202008%2C%20the%20SAMU%20had%20organized%20a%20month-long%20campaign%20on%20campus%2C%20Al-Haya%20Min%20Allah%2C%20against%20immorality.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20AMU%20official%2C%20speaking%20on%20the%20condition%20of%20anonymity%2C%20said%20the%20narrativ