of%20Alabama%20football%20coach%20Nick%20Saban%20is%20retiring%20after%2017%20seasons.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ESaban%20won%20six%20national%20titles%20with%20Alabama%20since%202007%2C%20with%20the%20most%20recent%20in%202017.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHe%20won%20more%20titles%20than%20any%20other%20major%20coach%20in%20college%20football.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ENick%20Saban%2C%20the%20stern%20coach%20who%20won%20seven%20national%20championships%20and%20turned%20Alabama%20back%20into%20a%20national%20powerhouse%20that%20included%20six%20of%20those%20titles%20in%20just%2017%20seasons%2C%20is%20retiring%2C%20according%20to%20multiple%20reports.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%2072-year-old%20Saban%20restored%20a%20Crimson%20Tide%20program%20once%20ruled%20by%20Paul%20%26quot%3BBear%26quot%3B%20Bryant%20to%20the%20top%20of%20college%20football%20after%20taking%20over%20in%202007.%20His%20decision%20to%20step%20away%20was%20reported%20Wednesday%2C%20first%20by%20ESPN%20and%20then%20by%20other%20outlets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESaban%20led%20the%20Crimson%20Tide%20from%20a%20shaky%20start%20this%20season%20to%20a%20Southeastern%20Conference%20championship%20and%20back%20into%20the%20College%20Football%20Playoff%20before%20falling%20to%20Michigan%20in%20a%20semifinal%20game%20at%20the%20Rose%20Bowl.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESaban%20led%20the%20Tide%20to%20nine%20Southeastern%20Conference%20championships%20and%20won%20his%20first%20national%20title%20at%20Alabama%20with%20a%2014-0%20season%20in%202009.%20Titles%20came%20again%20in%202011%2C%202012%2C%202015%2C%202017%20and%202020.%20Alabama%20was%20always%20a%20contender%20but%20had%20fallen%20short%20of%20the%20title%20since%20then.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESaban%20is%20famed%20for%20his%20sideline%20scowl%20and%20fiery%20demeanor%20%E2%80%94%20and%20for%20winning.%20Saban%20has%20won%20more%20national%20titles%20than%20any%20other%20major%20college%20coach.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20made%20a%20two-year%20foray%20into%20the%20NFL%20with%20the%20Miami%20Dolphins%20before%20r