0prison.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPhogat%20is%20among%20the%20main%20faces%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ftag%2Fwrestlers-protest%5C%22%3Elast%20year%E2%80%99s%20protests%20by%20prominent%20wrestlers%3C%2Fa%3E%20against%20BJP%20MP%20and%20former%20Wrestling%20Federation%20of%20India%20chief%20Brij%20Bhushan%20Sharan%20Singh%2C%20who%20is%20accused%20of%20sexually%20harassing%20at%20least%20seven%20wrestlers.%20Singh%20has%20denied%20the%20allegations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPhogat%20is%20also%20the%20first%20Indian%20woman%20wrestler%20to%20have%20won%20a%20gold%20at%20both%20the%20Commonwealth%20and%20Asian%20Games%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20only%20Indian%20woman%20wrestler%20to%20win%20multiple%20medals%20at%20the%20World%20Wrestling%20Championships.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20other%20news%20related%20to%20the%20Supreme%20Court%E2%80%99s%20judgement%20on%20Monday%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fcities%2Fahmedabad%2Fbilkis-bano-case-convicts-not-at-home-in-dahod-villages-families-tight-lipped-9100866%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EIndian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%20reports%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20nine%20of%20the%2011%20convicts%20in%20the%20case%20went%20%E2%80%9Cmissing%E2%80%9D%20from%20the%20twin%20villages%20of%20Randhikpur%20and%20Singvad%20in%20Gujarat%E2%80%99s%20Dahod%20district.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBano%20was%20also%20in%20Randhikpur%20when%20the%20Godhra%20train%20burning%2C%20which%20triggered%20the%202002%20riots%2C%20occurred.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%20%7C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fbilkis-bano-order-meaning-womens-rights-modi%5C%22%3ESix%20Things%3A%20Bilkis%20Bano%20Convicts%20Being%20Sent%20Back%20to%20Prison%20Is%20a%20Verdict%20on%20Much%20More%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAkhambhai%20Chaturbhai%20Raval%20(87)%2C%20father%20of%20one%20of%20the%20convicts%2C%20Govind%20Nai%20(55)%2C%20claimed%20his%20son%20was%20innocent%20and%20blamed%20the%20conviction%20on%20%E2%80%9Cpolitical%20vendetta%20of%C2%A0%5Bthe%5D%20Congress%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20told%20%3Cem%3EIE%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20Govind%20had%20left%20the%20house%20%E2%80%9Ca%20week%20ago%E2%80%9D.%20However%2C%20its%20report%20also%20cites%20a%20local%20policeman%20as%20saying%20that%20Nai%20had%20left%20home%20on%20Saturday%20(January%206).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20parents%20are%20reported%20as%20also%20saying%20they%20are%20a%20%E2%80%9CHindu%20faith-abiding%20family%2C%20incapable%20of%20committing%20the%20crimes%E2%80%9D%20that%20have%20been%20alleged%20against%20their%20son%20as%20well%20as%20against%20Nai%E2%80%99s%20uncle%20and%20Akhambhai%E2%80%99s%20brother%2C%20Jashvant%20Nai%2C%20who%20is%20another%20of%20the%2011%20convicts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20wish%20and%20pray%20that%20he%20%5BNai%5D%20gets%20to%20do%20%3Cem%3Eseva%3C%2Fem%3E%20%5Bservice%5D%20at%20the%20%5BRam%5D%20%3Cem%3Emandir%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3Epratishthan%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%20Ayodhya.%20It%20is%20better%20to%20do%20seva%20than%20do%20nothing%20and%20roam%20around%20every%20day.%20He%20has%20not%20been%20able%20to%20do%20anything%20since%20he%20was%20released%20%5Bfrom%20prison%5D%2C%E2%80%9D%20Raval%20was%20quoted%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CGoing%20back%20to%20jail%20is%20not%20a%20big%20deal%20and%20it%20is%20not%20that%20he%20was%20out%20of%20jail%20unlawfully.%20He%20was%20released%20with%20due%20process%20of%20law%20and%20now%20the%20law%20has%20told%20him%20to%20go%20back%2C%20so%20he%20will%20go%20back.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F18150906%2FSupreme-Court-1024x683.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%